y, WakaTime Invoicing simplifies time tracking and billing with automatic PDF invoicing. It\'s a great solution for freelancers who want to focus on their work and avoid the hassle of manual invoicing.','Freelancers Can Now Say Goodbye to Missing Billable Hours with Automated Developers Invoicing','','publish','open','open','','developers-invoicing','','','2023-02-28 08:19:09','2023-02-28 08:19:09','',0,'http://ec2-54-241-199-161.us-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com/?p=517',0,'post','',0),(518,1,'2023-02-27 12:32:07','2023-02-27 12:32:07','As a freelancer, keeping track of billable hours and creating invoices can be a real headache. Forgetting how much time was spent on a project or missing billable hours can lead to a loss of income and frustration. Alan, the creator of WakaTime, felt the same pain and decided to build a solution. He created WakaTime Invoicing, an automatic time tracking app that generates PDF invoices.\r\n\r\nWakaTime Invoicing is designed to know what you worked on, for how long, and fills out your PDF invoices automatically. The app uses your WakaTime code stats to detect the projects you\'ve worked on and the amount of time spent on each project. When it\'s time to bill your clients, WakaTime generates your pdf invoice, and you can be confident that you won\'t miss any billable hours.\r\n\r\nWith WakaTime Invoicing, you can focus on your work and let the app keep track of how long you worked. This can help you stay organized and avoid any missed billable hours. You can also be confident that your invoices are accurate and professional-looking.\r\n\r\nWakaTime Invoicing is easy to use. Simply let WakaTime run in the background, and when it\'s time to bill, your invoice is generated for you. You can also customize your invoice with your company logo and branding.\r\n\r\nAlan launched WakaTime Invoicing from code stats on Product Hunt today, and he would love an upvote from you! He highly recommends WakaTime Invoicing to anyone who wants to streamline 